description: Demolition of the existing buildings and redevelopment of the site comprising the erection of 4 to 9 storey building to provide 2,471sqm of flexible B1c workspace at ground and mezzanine level and 92 residential units (Use Class C3) on the upper floors, together with landscaped public open space, communal amenity space, on-site child play space, waste storage, cycle parking and disabled car parking.
